data.description: Welcome home! This charming and newly updated home was completely renovated in 2019. Updates include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, HVAC, water heater, siding and more. The spacious living area opens to a beautiful kitchen with gleaming white cabinets, black stainless appliances and the refrigerator stays! With the split bedroom floorplan, the master bedroom suite is a private retreat complete with a spacious bathroom with custom tiled shower.  Step outside to a large deck overlooking the backyard, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. A handy storage shed is included for lawn equipment and tools. This home is a blend of style, comfort, and modern amenities. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
